==The Mysterious Messenger==
* {{tcond|Delivering the letter for the first time:}}
** '''Messenger:''' I have a letter for you. I'm told it's quite important. Please read it when you get a chance.
** {{tact|An [[important letter]] is given to the player.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player destroys the letter without reading it:}}
** '''Messenger:''' Apparently you destroyed that last letter I gave you without reading it, or something like that. The sender doesn't appreciate that sort of thing, so I've got another one for you.
** {{tact|The [[important letter]] is given to the player again.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player destroys the letter without reading it for the second time:}}
** '''Messenger:''' Look, you can destroy that letter as many times as you want, but it won't change anything. The sender isn't the kind of individual who takes no for an answer, so for both of our sakes, please just read it.
** {{tact|The [[important letter]] is given to the player once more.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player destroys the letter without reading it for the third time:}}
** '''Messenger:''' Please... don't keep doing this. You don't know who you're dealing with...
** {{tact|The [[important letter]] is given to the player... again.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player destroys the letter without reading it for the fourth time:}}
** {{tbox|The messenger says nothing as he hands you another letter. However, the fear in his eyes is clear to see.}}
** {{tact|The [[important letter]] is, again, given to the player. The same message will be given if destroyed again without reading it.}}
** {{tact|end}}

